&quot;Music that has something to do with what you see&quot; has a long standing history in game use, but the specific bit about <em>using the PPU</em> implies using the one thing the PPU can do well: be a 4 bit DAC at 5MHz.<br /><br />Playing (optionally transformed) level data as sound is about as relevant to the PPU as it is to a beverage one might drink while playing.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3512">lidnariq</a> — Sat Nov 16, 2013 2:41 pm</p><hr />
