<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Intentional PPU hum...]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=5017&amp;p=120618#p120618"><![CDATA[
You're basically not going to be able to hear any difference as to where things are on the left or right side of the screen; your ears can't hear at those frequencies. All-in-all, it'll sound like a bunch of overtones of 60.1Hz, at varying strengths, and there will a strong correlation with total screen brightness and loudness.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3512">lidnariq</a> — Mon Nov 11, 2013 6:14 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
