I think I know how to get more bit depth. Vertical mirroring, black nametable 0, white nametable 1, use $2005 as if it were $4011. What this ends up doing is using the scroll to create pulse width modulation.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Sun May 12, 2013 12:59 pm</p><hr />
